    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="官方文档"><a href="#官方文档" class="headerlink" title="官方文档"></a>官方文档</h1><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>hexo.io<span class="hljs-regexp">/zh-cn/</span>docs<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="运行环境"><a href="#运行环境" class="headerlink" title="运行环境"></a>运行环境</h1><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mipsasm">git<br>node.<span class="hljs-keyword">js</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword"></span>hexo<br>gitee<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="git安装"><a href="#git安装" class="headerlink" title="git安装"></a>git安装</h1><h2 id="centos安装"><a href="#centos安装" class="headerlink" title="centos安装"></a>centos安装</h2><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">sudo yum <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> git-core<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="ubuntu安装"><a href="#ubuntu安装" class="headerlink" title="ubuntu安装"></a>ubuntu安装</h2><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">sudo apt <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> git-core<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装nodejs"><a href="#安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="安装nodejs"></a>安装nodejs</h1><h2 id="centos安装-1"><a href="#centos安装-1" class="headerlink" title="centos安装"></a>centos安装</h2><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">下载地址<br>http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>nodejs.cn/<br>可使用命令直接下载对应版本到当前目录 <span class="hljs-regexp">/usr/</span>share<br>wget https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>npm.taobao.org<span class="hljs-regexp">/mirrors/</span>node<span class="hljs-regexp">/v16.8.0/</span>node-v16.<span class="hljs-number">8.0</span>-linux-x64.tar.xz<br>解压<br>xz -d node-v12.<span class="hljs-number">16.1</span>-linux-x64.tar.xz<br>tar -xvf node-v12.<span class="hljs-number">16.1</span>-linux-x64.tar<br>部署bin文件并建立软连接<br>ln -s <span class="hljs-regexp">/usr/</span>share<span class="hljs-regexp">/node-v12.16.1-linux-x64/</span>bin<span class="hljs-regexp">/node /u</span>sr<span class="hljs-regexp">/local/</span>bin/node<br>ln -s <span class="hljs-regexp">/usr/</span>share<span class="hljs-regexp">/node-v12.16.1-linux-x64/</span>bin<span class="hljs-regexp">/npm /u</span>sr<span class="hljs-regexp">/local/</span>bin/npm<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="ubuntu安装-1"><a href="#ubuntu安装-1" class="headerlink" title="ubuntu安装"></a>ubuntu安装</h2><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">安装nvm<br>curl https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>raw.github.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/creationix/</span>nvm<span class="hljs-regexp">/master/i</span>nstall.sh | sh<br>安装完成后重启终端,运行以下命令<br>source ~/.profile<br>nvm install stable<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h1><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> -g hexo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="使用hexo"><a href="#使用hexo" class="headerlink" title="使用hexo"></a>使用hexo</h1><h2 id="初始化写作环境"><a href="#初始化写作环境" class="headerlink" title="初始化写作环境"></a>初始化写作环境</h2><figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gradle">创建文件夹<br>mkdir blogs<br>cd blogs<br>hexo  init<br>生成目录<br>.<br>├── _config.yml 网站的配置信息<br>├── <span class="hljs-keyword">package</span>.json  应用程序的信息<br>|-- <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Markdown和HTML文件会被解析并放到 <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span><br>├── scaffolds  模板文件<br>├── <span class="hljs-keyword">source</span><br>|   ├── _drafts<br>|   └── _posts  除 _posts文件夹之外，开头命名为 _(下划线)的文件/文件夹和隐藏的文件将会被忽略<br>└── themes  主题文件夹（https:<span class="hljs-comment">//hexo.io/themes/）</span><br><br>用git向gitee或github部署需要<br>npm install --save hexo-deployer-git<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
